[This is a very extensive and intensive epidemic of chikungunya. It
would be interesting to know if the Sri Lankan government is mounting
an intensive mosquito vector control campaign. A map of Sri Lanka can
be accessed at:
<http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/middle_east_and_asia/sri_lanka_pol01.jpg>.
